Don't you understand
how she must be feeling?

731
01:04:15,479 --> 01:04:18,789
Well. obviously
she's feeling sad about Cedric...

732
01:04:18,959 --> 01:04:21,917
...and confused about liking Harry
and guilty about kissing him...

733
01:04:22,080 --> 01:04:25,152
...conflicted because Umbridge might
sack her mum from the Ministry...

734
01:04:25,319 --> 01:04:28,914
...and frightened of failing her OWLs
because she's worrying about everything.

735
01:04:30,759 --> 01:04:34,195
One person couldn't feel all that.
They'd explode.

736
01:04:34,359 --> 01:04:37,476
Just because you've got
the emotional range of a teaspoon....

737
01:04:52,760 --> 01:04:54,239
Harry.

738
01:05:02,639 --> 01:05:05,597
Voldemort may be after something.

739
01:05:06,239 --> 01:05:09,117
Something he didn't have last time.

740
01:05:09,919 --> 01:05:11,113
Harry.

741
01:05:12,679 --> 01:05:13,907
Harry.

742
01:05:43,719 --> 01:05:46,995
In the dream.
were you standing next to the victim...

743
01:05:47,159 --> 01:05:48,592
...or looking down at the scene?

744
01:05:49,040 --> 01:05:51,873
Neither. It was like I....

745
01:05:52,440 --> 01:05:54,431
Will you please just tell me
what's happening?

746
01:05:54,600 --> 01:05:56,830
Everard. Arthur's on guard duty
tonight.

747
01:05:57,000 --> 01:05:59,309
Make sure he's found
by the right people.

748
01:05:59,479 --> 01:06:00,992
-Sir.
-Phineas.

749
01:06:01,160 --> 01:06:03,355
You must go to your portrait
at Grimmauld Place.

750
01:06:03,519 --> 01:06:06,033
Tell them that Arthur Weasley
is gravely injured...

751
01:06:06,199 --> 01:06:10,192
...and his children will be arriving there
soon by Portkey.

752
01:06:10,360 --> 01:06:13,318
They've got him. Albus. It was close.
but they think he'll make it.

753
01:06:13,480 --> 01:06:15,869
What's more.
the Dark Lord failed to acquire it.

754
01:06:16,039 --> 01:06:17,870
Oh. thank goodness. Next we need to--

755
01:06:18,039 --> 01:06:19,188
Look at me!

756
01:06:25,440 --> 01:06:27,556
What's happening to me?

757
01:06:35,119 --> 01:06:36,916
You wished to see me. headmaster?

758
01:06:37,079 --> 01:06:41,789
Oh. Severus. I'm afraid we can't wait.
Not even till the morning.

759
01:06:42,159 --> 01:06:44,957
Otherwise. we'll all be vulnerable.

760
01:06:49,520 --> 01:06:51,078
It appears there's a connection...

761
01:06:51,240 --> 01:06:53,470
...between the Dark Lord's mind
and your own.

762
01:06:53,640 --> 01:06:57,633
Whether he is. as yet. aware of this
connection is. for the moment. unclear.

763
01:06:57,960 --> 01:07:00,872
Pray he remains ignorant.

764
01:07:01,040 --> 01:07:04,191
You mean. if he knows about it. then...

765
01:07:04,639 --> 01:07:08,837
-...he'll be able to read my mind?
-Read it. control it...

766
01:07:08,999 --> 01:07:10,796
...unhinge it.

767
01:07:10,959 --> 01:07:14,190
In the past. it was often
the Dark Lord's pleasure...

768
01:07:14,360 --> 01:07:16,510
...to invade the minds of his victims...

769
01:07:16,679 --> 01:07:20,115
...creating visions designed
to torture them into madness.

770
01:07:21,199 --> 01:07:25,795
Only after extracting the last exquisite
ounce of agony...

771
01:07:25,959 --> 01:07:30,077
...only when he had them literally
begging for death. would he finally...

772
01:07:30,239 --> 01:07:31,388
...kill them.

773
01:07:32,360 --> 01:07:34,669
Used properly.
the power of Occlumency...

774
01:07:34,840 --> 01:07:38,196
...will help shield you
from access or influence.

775
01:07:38,360 --> 01:07:42,911
In these lessons. I will attempt
to penetrate your mind.

776
01:07:43,480 --> 01:07:46,438
You will attempt to resist.

777
01:07:46,719 --> 01:07:48,118
Prepare yourself.

778
01:07:50,760 --> 01:07:51,909
l.egilimens.

779
01:07:59,719 --> 01:08:03,155
Concentrate. Potter. Focus.

780
01:08:28,000 --> 01:08:29,558
Ho, ho, ho. Merry Christmas.

781
01:08:30,720 --> 01:08:33,280
Here we go.

782
01:08:33,439 --> 01:08:35,509
Daddy's back.

783
01:08:38,560 --> 01:08:42,030
Sit down. everybody. sit down.
That's it. Now. presents.

784
01:08:42,200 --> 01:08:46,398
-And a nice big box for Ron.
-Big box for you. And....

785
01:08:49,080 --> 01:08:51,196
Fred and George. Come on. open up.

786
01:08:51,360 --> 01:08:53,555
-I want to see your faces.
-Yes.

787
01:08:53,719 --> 01:08:56,028
-Try it on.
-Thanks. Mum. It's perfect.

788
01:08:56,199 --> 01:09:00,317
-Just what he wanted. actually.
-Yeah. Right. Thanks. Mum.

789
01:09:00,480 --> 01:09:03,233
Come on. then. everybody.
Let's clear this away.

790
01:09:03,399 --> 01:09:05,310
Oh. Harry. Harry.

791
01:09:05,480 --> 01:09:07,311
There you are.

792
01:09:08,279 --> 01:09:10,031
-Happy Christmas.
-Thank you.

793
01:09:10,599 --> 01:09:12,351
-Love|y to have you with us.
-Thank you.

794
01:09:12,520 --> 01:09:14,431
Now. Daddy. Pass that to Daddy.

795
01:09:14,599 --> 01:09:16,237
-Thank you.
-Has everybody got?

796
01:09:16,399 --> 01:09:17,718
Fred? George?

797
01:09:17,879 --> 01:09:20,313
-Hermione.
-A Christmas toast.

798
01:09:20,479 --> 01:09:22,276
To Mr. Harry Potter...

799
01:09:23,240 --> 01:09:25,959
...without whom I would not be here.

800
01:09:29,399 --> 01:09:31,629
-Harry.
-Harry.

801
01:09:31,800 --> 01:09:32,994
Harry.

802
01:09:33,960 --> 01:09:36,428
That is delicious.
I shall be needing some more of that.

803
01:09:36,600 --> 01:09:38,875
Daddy. don't forget last Christmas.

804
01:09:39,760 --> 01:09:42,399
I can't understand
why you don't want to wear it. Ronald.

805
01:09:43,800 --> 01:09:45,552
I look like a bloody idiot. that's why.

806
01:09:45,720 --> 01:09:47,472
No more than usual. Ron.

807
01:09:47,680 --> 01:09:49,432
I don't know why....

808
01:09:55,200 --> 01:09:59,591
Nasty brat. standing there
as bold as brass.

809
01:09:59,759 --> 01:10:04,310
Harry Potter.
the boy who stopped the Dark Lord.

810
01:10:04,480 --> 01:10:07,358
Friend of Mudbloods
and blood-traitors alike.

811
01:10:07,760 --> 01:10:10,274
-If my poor mistress only knew....
-Kreacher!

812
01:10:10,439 --> 01:10:13,158
That's enough of your bile.
Away with you!

813
01:10:13,320 --> 01:10:15,231
Of course. master.

814
01:10:15,399 --> 01:10:19,870
Kreacher lives to serve
the noble house of Black.

815
01:10:22,119 --> 01:10:23,916
Sorry about that.

816
01:10:24,480 --> 01:10:27,995
He never was very pleasant.
even when I was a boy.

817
01:10:28,320 --> 01:10:30,311
Not to me. anyway.

818
01:10:31,119 --> 01:10:32,996
What. you grew up here?

819
01:10:33,160 --> 01:10:35,310
This is my parents' house.

820
01:10:35,639 --> 01:10:39,314
I offered it to Dumbledore
as headquarters for the Order.

821
01:10:40,399 --> 01:10:43,550
About the only useful thing
I've been able to do.

822
01:10:44,879 --> 01:10:47,154
This is the Black family tree.

823
01:10:48,039 --> 01:10:50,075
My deranged cousin.

824
01:10:50,240 --> 01:10:52,834
I hated the lot of them.

825
01:10:52,999 --> 01:10:57,515
My parents with their pure-blood mania.

826
01:11:00,600 --> 01:11:04,229
My mother did that after I ran away.

827
01:11:06,480 --> 01:11:08,277
Charming woman.

828
01:11:09,480 --> 01:11:11,072
I was 16.

829
01:11:11,879 --> 01:11:13,232
Where did you go?

830
01:11:15,240 --> 01:11:16,434
Round your dad's.

831
01:11:17,879 --> 01:11:20,313
I was always welcome at the Potters'.

832
01:11:21,160 --> 01:11:23,799
I see him so much in you. Harry.

833
01:11:24,399 --> 01:11:26,515
You are so very much alike.

834
01:11:27,399 --> 01:11:29,310
I'm not so sure.

835
01:11:30,320 --> 01:11:31,719
Sirius. when I was....

836
01:11:34,439 --> 01:11:38,751
When I saw Mr. Weasley attacked.
I wasn't just watching.

837
01:11:39,880 --> 01:11:41,313
I was the snake.

838
01:11:42,119 --> 01:11:44,952
And afterwards.
in Dumbledore's office...

839
01:11:45,120 --> 01:11:49,159
...there was a moment
when I wanted to--

840
01:11:54,079 --> 01:11:56,832
This connection
between me and Voldemort.

841
01:11:57,480 --> 01:12:00,916
What if the reason for it
is that I am becoming more like him?

842
01:12:02,199 --> 01:12:06,909
I just feel so angry all the time.

843
01:12:07,080 --> 01:12:11,437
And what if. after everything
that I've been through...

844
01:12:11,599 --> 01:12:15,035
...something's gone wrong inside me?
What if I'm becoming bad?

845
01:12:17,559 --> 01:12:20,676
I want you to listen to me
very carefully. Harry.

846
01:12:21,800 --> 01:12:24,678
You're not a bad person.

847
01:12:25,480 --> 01:12:29,632
You're a very good person
who bad things have happened to.

848
01:12:30,240 --> 01:12:31,309
You understand?

849
01:12:33,320 --> 01:12:38,155
Besides. the world isn't split
into good people and Death Eaters.

850
01:12:38,319 --> 01:12:42,597
We've all got both light and dark
inside of us.

851
01:12:43,319 --> 01:12:46,436
What matters
is the part we choose to act on.

852
01:12:48,320 --> 01:12:50,515
That's who we really are.

853
01:12:54,120 --> 01:12:55,792
Harry. time to go.

854
01:12:57,480 --> 01:13:01,598
When all this is over.
we'll be a proper family.

855
01:13:01,760 --> 01:13:03,273
You'll see.

856
01:13:04,360 --> 01:13:05,679
Come on.

857
01:13:41,600 --> 01:13:42,715
ReaHy?

858
01:13:42,880 --> 01:13:45,394
Harry. Harry.

859
01:13:45,560 --> 01:13:47,391
Hagrid's back.

860
01:13:50,240 --> 01:13:51,992
I'm sorry.

861
01:14:05,639 --> 01:14:08,676
I will say this one last time.

862
01:14:08,960 --> 01:14:11,235
I'm ordering you to tell me
where you've been.

863
01:14:11,399 --> 01:14:14,277
I told you. I've been away
for me health.

864
01:14:14,600 --> 01:14:18,593
-Your health?
-Yeah. Bit of fresh air. you know.

865
01:14:18,759 --> 01:14:23,389
Oh. yes. As gamekeeper.
fresh air must be difficult to come by.

866
01:14:25,360 --> 01:14:27,749
If I were you.
I shouldn't get too used to being back.

867
01:14:27,919 --> 01:14:31,070
In fact. I mightn't bother
unpacking at all.

868
01:14:49,240 --> 01:14:52,198
This is top-secret. right?

869
01:14:53,079 --> 01:14:55,354
Dumbledore sent me
to parley with the giants.

870
01:14:55,519 --> 01:14:56,952
Giants?

871
01:14:58,120 --> 01:14:59,109
You found them?

872
01:14:59,279 --> 01:15:02,988
Well, they're not that hard to find. to be
perfectly honest. They're so big. see?

873
01:15:03,839 --> 01:15:06,751
I tried to convince them
to join the cause.

874
01:15:06,919 --> 01:15:09,479
But I wasn't the only one
that was trying to win them over.

875
01:15:10,160 --> 01:15:11,991
-Death Eaters?
-Yes.

876
01:15:12,440 --> 01:15:15,637
Trying to persuade them
to join You-Know-Who.

877
01:15:16,120 --> 01:15:18,395
-Did they?
-I gave them Dumbledore's message.

878
01:15:18,560 --> 01:15:22,473
Suppose some of them remember
he was friendly to them. I suppose.

879
01:15:25,959 --> 01:15:27,187
And they did this to you?

880
01:15:27,880 --> 01:15:29,552
Not exactly. no.

881
01:15:30,040 --> 01:15:33,794
Oh, go on, you have it, then,
you dozy dog.

882
01:15:47,199 --> 01:15:49,235
It's changing out there.

883
01:15:49,639 --> 01:15:51,152
Just like last time.

884
01:15:52,560 --> 01:15:54,118
There's a storm coming. Harry.

885
01:15:54,839 --> 01:15:57,797
We'd all best be ready when she does.

886
01:16:33,279 --> 01:16:36,191
We have confirmed
that 10 high-security prisoners...

887
01:16:36,360 --> 01:16:39,079
...in the early hours of yesterday evening
did escape.

888
01:16:39,239 --> 01:16:42,754
And of course, the Muggle prime minister
has been alerted to the danger.

889
01:16:42,919 --> 01:16:44,910
We strongly suspect. . .

890
01:16:45,720 --> 01:16:47,631
...that the breakout was engineered...

891
01:16:47,799 --> 01:16:51,838
...by a man with personal experience
in escaping from Azkaban...

892
01:16:51,999 --> 01:16:56,038
...notorious mass murderer Sirius Black...

893
01:16:57,440 --> 01:17:01,638
...cousin of escapee
Bella trix Les trange.

894
01:17:11,520 --> 01:17:13,715
Dumbledore warned Fudge
this could happen.

895
01:17:13,880 --> 01:17:16,917
He's gonna get us all killed
just because he can't face the truth.

896
01:17:17,080 --> 01:17:18,149
Harry.

897
01:17:21,720 --> 01:17:23,631
I wanted to apologize.

898
01:17:24,200 --> 01:17:28,193
Now even me mum says the Prophet's
version of things don't add up.

899
01:17:28,360 --> 01:17:34,037
So. what I'm really trying to say
is that I believe you.

900
01:17:40,679 --> 01:17:42,237
Neville?

901
01:17:54,280 --> 01:17:56,350
Fourteen years ago...

902
01:17:56,520 --> 01:18:00,593
...a Death Eater
named Bellatrix Lestrange...

903
01:18:00,759 --> 01:18:03,831
...used a Cruciatus Curse
on my parents.

904
01:18:04,360 --> 01:18:08,194
She tortured them for information...

905
01:18:08,360 --> 01:18:10,430
...but they never gave in.

906
01:18:12,040 --> 01:18:14,429
I'm quite proud to be their son.

907
01:18:15,360 --> 01:18:19,069
But I'm not sure I'm ready
for everyone to know just yet.

908
01:18:24,759 --> 01:18:28,718
We're gonna make them proud. Neville.
That's a promise.

909
01:18:32,800 --> 01:18:36,349
Make it a powerful memory.
the happiest you can remember.

910
01:18:36,519 --> 01:18:39,795
Allow it to fill you up.
Keep trying. Seamus.

911
01:18:39,960 --> 01:18:41,313
George. your turn now.

912
01:18:42,600 --> 01:18:44,830
Expecto Patronum.

913
01:18:45,720 --> 01:18:48,996
A full-bodied Patronus
is the most difficult to produce...

914
01:18:49,160 --> 01:18:52,835
...but shield forms can also be equally
useful against a variety of opponents.

915
01:18:52,999 --> 01:18:54,193
Wow. that was really good.

916
01:18:54,880 --> 01:18:56,359
Fantastic. Ginny.

917
01:18:56,520 --> 01:19:00,399
Just remember. your Patronus can only
protect you for as long as you stay focused.

918
01:19:00,559 --> 01:19:02,754
So focus. Luna.

919
01:19:06,319 --> 01:19:07,957
Think of the happiest thing you can.

920
01:19:08,119 --> 01:19:09,996
Expecto Patronum.

921
01:19:10,160 --> 01:19:12,913
-|'m trying.
-I know. It's good.

922
01:19:13,080 --> 01:19:17,153
This is really advanced stuff. guys.
You're doing so well.

923
01:19:17,880 --> 01:19:20,189
Expecto Patronum.

924
01:20:00,319 --> 01:20:02,753
I'll make short work of this.

925
01:20:04,040 --> 01:20:05,951
Bombarda Maxima.

926
01:20:23,480 --> 01:20:24,799
Get them.

927
01:20:25,200 --> 01:20:26,599
Been watching them for weeks.

928
01:20:26,760 --> 01:20:28,637
And see. “Dumbledore's Army“...

929
01:20:29,040 --> 01:20:32,589
...proof of what I've been telling you
right from the beginning. Cornelius.

930
01:20:33,920 --> 01:20:35,876
All your fear-mongering
about You-Know-Who...

931
01:20:36,040 --> 01:20:37,519
...never fooled us for a minute.

932
01:20:37,679 --> 01:20:39,670
We saw your lies for what they were:

933
01:20:39,840 --> 01:20:43,469
A smokescreen for your bid
to seize control of the Ministry.

934
01:20:43,639 --> 01:20:44,628
Naturally.

935
01:20:44,800 --> 01:20:47,234
No. professor.
He had nothing to do with it. It was me.

936
01:20:47,400 --> 01:20:50,915
Most noble of you. Harry. to shield me.
but as has been pointed out...

937
01:20:51,080 --> 01:20:55,710
...the parchment clearly says
“Dumbledore's Army." not “Potter's.“

938
01:20:55,879 --> 01:20:58,393
I instructed Harry
to form this organization.

939
01:20:58,559 --> 01:21:01,869
And I. and I alone.
am responsible for its activities.

940
01:21:02,040 --> 01:21:03,792
Dispatch an ow! to the Daily Prophet.

941
01:21:03,960 --> 01:21:06,394
If we hurry. we should still make
the morning edition.

942
01:21:06,559 --> 01:21:11,155
Dawlish. Shacklebolt.
you will escort Dumbledore...

943
01:21:11,319 --> 01:21:12,672
...to Azkaban...

944
01:21:13,879 --> 01:21:18,828
...to await trial
for conspiracy and sedition.

945
01:21:18,999 --> 01:21:21,797
I thought we might hit this little snag.

946
01:21:22,920 --> 01:21:26,230
You seem to be laboring
under the delusion that I'm going to--

947
01:21:26,760 --> 01:21:28,159
What was the phrase?

948
01:21:28,320 --> 01:21:29,833
--come quietly.

949
01:21:30,000 --> 01:21:31,638
Well. I can tell you this:

950
01:21:32,039 --> 01:21:34,269
I have no intention
of going to Azkaban.

951
01:21:34,439 --> 01:21:35,633
Enough of this.

952
01:21:36,120 --> 01:21:37,155
Take him.

953
01:21:49,480 --> 01:21:53,678
Well. you may not like him. minister...

954
01:21:53,840 --> 01:21:55,876
...but you can't deny...

955
01:21:56,399 --> 01:21:59,038
...Dumbledore has got style.

956
01:22:22,120 --> 01:22:26,591
Boys and girls are not permitted
to be within eight inches of each other.

957
01:22:26,760 --> 01:22:30,036
Those wishing to join
the Inquisitorial Squad for extra credit....

958
01:22:30,199 --> 01:22:35,034
Students will be submitted to questioning
about suspected illicit activities.

959
01:22:35,200 --> 01:22:39,318
Any student in noncompliance
will be expelled.

960
01:23:47,600 --> 01:23:49,158
Harry.

961
01:23:55,799 --> 01:23:59,075
You did everything you could.
No one could win against that old hag.

962
01:23:59,240 --> 01:24:01,470
Even Dumbledore
didn't see this coming.

963
01:24:02,360 --> 01:24:04,430
Harry. if it's anyone's fault. it's ours.

964
01:24:04,600 --> 01:24:06,591
Yeah. we talked you into it.

965
01:24:06,760 --> 01:24:08,671
Yeah. but I agreed.

966
01:24:09,199 --> 01:24:13,158
I tried so hard to help.
and all it's done is make things worse.

967
01:24:15,119 --> 01:24:17,474
Anyway. that doesn't matter anymore.

968
01:24:18,479 --> 01:24:22,518
Because I don't want to play anymore.
All it does is make you care too much.

969
01:24:22,680 --> 01:24:25,240
And the more you care.
the more you have to lose.

970
01:24:25,399 --> 01:24:28,436
-So maybe it's just better to....
-To what?

971
01:24:30,599 --> 01:24:32,430
To go it alone.

972
01:24:38,520 --> 01:24:40,112
Hagrid.

973
01:24:43,720 --> 01:24:46,029
Any idea where he's taking us?

974
01:24:46,199 --> 01:24:49,157
Hagrid. why can't you just tell us?

975
