without telling someone about him.

984
01:25:27,880 --> 01:25:29,472
Grawpy.

985
01:25:31,760 --> 01:25:33,796
Down here. you great buffoon.

986
01:25:39,880 --> 01:25:41,472
Grawpy.

987
01:25:42,239 --> 01:25:43,877
Brought you some company.

988
01:25:55,720 --> 01:25:57,870
