exactly the same thing.

1056
01:32:04,319 --> 01:32:05,911
All right. professor!

1057
01:32:14,319 --> 01:32:16,037
Here you go.

1058
01:32:39,959 --> 01:32:41,711
Ready when you are.

1059
01:34:03,959 --> 01:34:07,076
I need that prophecy.

1060
01:34:07,240 --> 01:34:08,992
