I saw it. It's just like
with Mr. Weasley.

1067
01:34:36,239 --> 01:34:38,036
It's the door I've been dreaming about.

1068
01:34:38,200 --> 01:34:40,191
I couldn't remember
where I'd seen it before.

1069
01:34:40,360 --> 01:34:42,191
Sirius said Voldemort
was after something.

1070
01:34:42,359 --> 01:34:45,510
