weren't you?

1087
01:35:49,159 --> 01:35:51,070
-No.
-Liar.

1088
01:35:51,239 --> 01:35:53,958
-You sent for me. headmistress?
-Snape. yes.

1089
01:35:54,119 --> 01:35:57,475
