1103
01:36:47,760 --> 01:36:50,593
As this is an issue
of Ministry security...

1104
01:36:50,760 --> 01:36:52,751
...you leave me with...

1105
01:36:53,480 --> 01:36:55,357
...no alternative.

1106
01:36:56,120 --> 01:36:58,236
The Cruciatus Curse
ought to loosen your tongue.

1107
01:36:58,399 --> 01:36:59,388
That's illegal.

1108
01:36:59,560 --> 01:37:02,757
What Cornelius doesn't know
won't hurt him.

1109
01:37:09,959 --> 01:37:11,392
Tell her. Harry!

1110
01:37:12,839 --> 01:37:14,238
Tell me what?

1111
01:37:15,399 --> 01:37:17,310
Well. if you won't tell her where it is...

1112
01:37:17,959 --> 01:37:19,631
...I will.

1113
01:37:21,199 --> 01:37:22,917
Where what is?

1114
01:37:24,079 --> 01:37:26,274
Dumbledore's secret weapon.

1115
01:37:31,079 --> 01:37:32,558
How much further?

1116
01:37:32,719 --> 01:37:34,311
Not far.

1117
01:37:36,239 --> 01:37:39,788
It had to be somewhere
students wouldn't find it accidentally.

1118
01:37:43,960 --> 01:37:45,359
What are you doing?

1119
01:37:45,520 --> 01:37:47,238
Improvising.

1120
01:37:55,399 --> 01:37:56,957
Well?

1121
01:37:58,199 --> 01:38:00,235
Where is this weapon?

1122
01:38:04,960 --> 01:38:07,110
