This is a Ministry matter.

1127
01:38:42,439 --> 01:38:44,031
Lower your weapons.

1128
01:38:44,200 --> 01:38:49,513
I warn you. under the law. as
creatures of near-human intelligence....

1129
01:38:49,679 --> 01:38:50,873
