1135
01:39:24,279 --> 01:39:26,747
You filthy animal.

1136
01:39:26,920 --> 01:39:29,753
Do you know who I am?

1137
01:39:29,920 --> 01:39:32,639
Leave him alone. It's not his fault.

1138
01:39:32,800 --> 01:39:34,597
No. he doesn't understand.

1139
01:39:41,960 --> 01:39:45,270
Potter. do something.
Tell them I mean no harm.

1140
01:39:45,440 --> 01:39:47,271
l' m sorry. professor.

1141
01:39:47,440 --> 01:39:49,158
But I must not tell lies.

1142
01:39:49,320 --> 01:39:50,309
